  [2]: https://docs.spring.io/spring-security/site/docs/current/api/org/springframework/security/web/util/matcher/AntPathRequestMatcher.html
  [3]: https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-framework/issues/17876
  [4]: https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-security/issues/2355

